{"tid":1866391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國財長：肺炎疫情不會影響中國履行貿易協議承諾","createTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T01:55:23.000Z","uid":125193,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0197dc672e893e410db60382e16eafe2ee41e7","tid":1866391,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507112-20200206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507112-20200206.htm&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=12044c78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507112-20200206.htm&h=d39f7fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507112-20200206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ec23259e2ec20ca021556ecb90e47fd56dfa4256","tid":1866391,"uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"美國財長努欽表示，雖然中國爆發新型冠狀病毒疫情，已導致數百人死亡，亦會對中國經濟造成重大影響，但他預期，疫情不會影響中國履行貿易協議的承諾。努欽表示，中國在未來兩年將對美國商品和服務的採購量，增加至少2千億美元。努欽又表示，目前仍未看到供應鏈方面出現重大問題，但美方會密切關注。<br />\n<br />\n在中美第一階段貿易協議中，中國承諾曾購美國商品，不過，內地環球時報表示，中國可能正考慮使用協議中的災難相關條款，允許延後執行協議。"},{"pid":"7efa4eadef295ca9322aad27f5734e2cec449192","tid":1866391,"uid":198783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994b9e4bf8b8d692090aa5fbe1415f59f2662949","tid":1866391,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"都知你支共要屠自己班支那豬整苦肉計架啦<br />\n點會咁天真心軟"},{"pid":"fb364305b087be9f295afe57275d58706337ce2e","